Class BruteForceFallbackTheory

  • java.lang.Object

    @Beta
public class BruteForceFallbackTheory
extends TheoryWrapper
    A Theory that passes all methods through to a base theory, but wraps StepSolvers in BruteForceFallbackQuantifierEliminationStepSolverWrapper.
